00:30:55,360 --> 00:30:56,250
What?

591
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:58,650
My gear.

592
00:31:01,930 --> 00:31:03,120
Is that all you think about?

593
00:31:03,490 --> 00:31:04,890
It's in my car.

594
00:31:05,490 --> 00:31:06,450
You collapsed,

595
00:31:06,450 --> 00:31:07,560
and you're still thinking about the gear?

596
00:31:08,490 --> 00:31:09,080
I'll call the team

597
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:10,170
and have it

598
00:31:10,170 --> 00:31:11,120
