600
00:31:16,730 --> 00:31:17,800
I didn't have time to tell anyone.

601
00:31:18,010 --> 00:31:19,040
After you collapsed,

602
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,760
I only told Zhan Yan.

603
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:22,690
Want me to

604
00:31:22,690 --> 00:31:23,560
call the team members?

605
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:24,170
OK.

606
00:31:24,490 --> 00:31:25,080
No.

607
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:25,930
No, thanks.

608
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:29,080
I'm good.

609
00:31:29,650 --> 00:31:31,600
I didn't sleep well,

610
