611
00:31:33,970 --> 00:31:35,560
Alright, I'm off.

612
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:36,760
I've got business to do.

613
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:37,560
Wait a minute.

614
00:31:37,560 --> 00:31:38,600
Where are you going?

615
00:31:40,930 --> 00:31:41,450
Lie down.

616
00:31:41,560 --> 00:31:43,040
I-I'm going to the bathroom.

617
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:44,080
Lie down.

618
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:45,970
Lie down.

619
00:31:46,490 --> 00:31:47,080
Listen.

620
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:50,040
I-I'm okay.

621
00:31:50,250 --> 00:31:51,930
I'm now informing you

622
00:31:51,930 --> 00:31:53,080
as a doctor

623
00:31:53,490 --> 00:31:54,560
that you'll have an operation tomorrow.

624
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:58,320
It's no big deal. An operation?

625
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:59,080
No.

626
00:31:59,080 --> 00:32:00,650
I know what

627
00:32:00,650 --> 00:32:01,890
problem I have.

628
00:32:01,890 --> 00:32:03,210
You know?

629
00:32:04,210 --> 00:32:06,080
Then why are you still
on the rescue team?

630
00:32:07,360 --> 00:32:09,450
It's just a tumor. You…

631
00:32:11,410 --> 00:32:11,970
You…

632
00:32:12,080 --> 00:32:14,170
I have it checked, a benign one.

633
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:15,170
Who told you

634
00:32:15,170 --> 00:32:16,320
that a benign tumor was safe?

635
00:32:19,010 --> 00:32:20,280
Can I not have an operation?

636
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:21,320
I'll be careful.

637
00:32:22,210 --> 00:32:22,690
No.

638
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:24,040
I think

639
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:25,080
you should listen to Dr. Zhan.

640
00:32:25,730 --> 00:32:27,360
I've got work to do.

641
00:32:27,450 --> 00:32:28,360
If you refuse to listen,

642
00:32:28,360 --> 00:32:28,930
I will

643
00:32:28,930 --> 00:32:30,320
tell your captain immediately.

644
00:32:30,520 --> 00:32:30,930
No, no.

645
00:32:31,170 --> 00:32:32,490
Please don't.

646
00:32:32,930 --> 00:32:34,410
He mustn't know this.

647
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:35,320
How about this?

648
00:32:36,170 --> 00:32:37,280
Let's make a deal.

649
00:32:37,450 --> 00:32:39,080
You don't tell the captain

650
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,450
and everybody else on the team,

651
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:41,760
and I'll have the operation.

652
00:32:42,410 --> 00:32:43,170
Otherwise,

653
00:32:44,250 --> 00:32:45,080
I won't do it.

654
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,450
I'll arrange your
physical examination.

655
00:33:01,970 --> 00:33:03,080
You knew

656
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:04,080
you were ill long ago.

657
00:33:14,410 --> 00:33:15,930
So it has always been water

658
00:33:16,170 --> 00:33:17,560
in the flask.

659
00:33:19,120 --> 00:33:21,360
I almost lost this baby.

660
00:33:26,450 --> 00:33:28,040
You keep the secret for me, kiddo.

661
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:29,840
Tell nobody

662
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:31,760
that I'll have an operation.

663
00:33:31,930 --> 00:33:33,120
If anybody asks,

664
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,210
just say I'm tired

665
00:33:35,210 --> 00:33:36,210
and resting at home.

666
00:33:36,450 --> 00:33:37,210
Go, now.

667
00:33:37,890 --> 00:33:39,040
You just lie down.

668
00:33:39,930 --> 00:33:42,450
Don't worry, I'm a lawyer.
And a lawyer doesn't snitch.

669
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:45,930
All right. Just go. Go.

670
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:47,800
I've got a whole bunch of doctors

671
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,250
and nurses to look after me.

672
00:33:48,320 --> 00:33:49,560
I don't need you here.

673
00:33:49,760 --> 00:33:51,080
You'll have your test tomorrow.

674
00:33:57,890 --> 00:33:58,650
What?

675
00:33:59,250 --> 00:34:00,170
You're chickening out?

676
00:34:01,490 --> 00:34:03,210
I'm not even sure

677
00:34:03,210 --> 00:34:04,120
