678
00:34:06,250 --> 00:34:07,930
It doesn't sound like

679
00:34:07,930 --> 00:34:09,040
something that you'd say,
Mr. Luo, the lawyer.

680
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:10,120
What?

681
00:34:10,370 --> 00:34:11,600
If you don't show up,

682
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:12,810
