What are we doing here?

712
00:36:15,810 --> 00:36:17,240
Whenever I feel

713
00:36:17,240 --> 00:36:17,970
troubled,

714
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:19,770
I'll come here to sing songs.

715
00:36:20,290 --> 00:36:22,120
So you brought me here
to sing songs?

716
00:36:23,970 --> 00:36:24,890
A doctor

717
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:26,410
needs to learn

718
00:36:26,410 --> 00:36:27,890
to adjust their emotions

719
00:36:27,890 --> 00:36:28,560
to better

720
00:36:28,560 --> 00:36:29,560
treat the patients.

721
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,810
My emotions are stable.

722
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:33,490
Just give it a go.

723
00:36:33,930 --> 00:36:34,720
No.

724
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:36,010
It works great.

725
00:36:36,490 --> 00:36:37,010
Come on.

726
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:40,290
In you go.

